displaytags template plugin
===========================

Tag provides a template plugin that you can use in your template to display
the tags for your content item if you don't wish to (or cannot) rely on the
display hooks. The plugin is available globally.

Call the plugin in your template like so:

{displaytags modname='News' objectid=$info.sid areaname='subscriber.news.ui_hooks.articles'}

modname is the module name
objectid is the id of the object
areaname is the **subscriber** hook areaname for **your** module.
See your module's Version.php and use the **Bundle** areaname for the ui_hooks bundle.